The Trial Chamber of the Extraordinary Chambers in the Courts of Cambodia (ECCC) has decided to make public the video recording of the morning session of the Trial Management Meeting in Case 002/02 that was held on 28 October 2014.
The session made public relates to discussions on the resources made available to the Defence teams for Khieu Samphan and Nuon Chea, and under what conditions the defence teams would be ready to participate in the Case 002/02 trial hearings. 
The parties also made submissions related to a proposal from the Co-Prosecutors to appoint amici curiae counsel to safeguard the interest of the accused in the event that their co-lawyers continue to be absent from trial hearings.